Required Addons
1. Stock Cycle Count
2. Inventory Lock Down
3. Stock Inventory Verification Request
4. Stock Inventory Discrepancy
5. Stock Inventory Exclude Sublocation

How
1. Go to Inventory > Configuration > Cycle Count Rules. Create as much cycle count rules as you want.
2. Go to Inventory > Configuration > Warehouse Management > Warehouses and set a Cycle Count Planning Horizon for each warehouse. Only the counts in the horizon will be created.
